      "span_text": "Second, we adjusted for age, gender, income, stratum (city or suburban), the number of severe chronic conditions, BMI, smoking status, and risk of alcohol abuse since these covariates were associated with inflammatory markers. [CITATION_1] When examining census-tract poverty rate, we used a twolevel model with the random components assessed at the individual and censustract level.",
